snippet.title: Enhanced Amber Portwood Audio Christmas Eve 2018
snippet.description:
Audio of a altercation that took place on Christmas Eve at Amber Portwoods home between Amber and then Boyfriend Andrew Glennon was given to Katie Joy from Without A Crystal Ball on 9/13/2019. 
Katie Joy was given permission to release this audio by a family member or family friend of Andrew Glennon. This audio is not and will not be used in any court proceedings between Amber and Andrew. This audio has been enhanced so we can hear the voices more clearly. We also added subtitles for the hearing impaired. 
Katie Joy From Without a Crystal Ball has the original audio and if you like to listen to it please check out her channel. 


 WARNING: IF YOU SUFFER FROM PTSD OR HAVE BEEN A VICTIM OF DOMESTIC ABUSE THIS COULD POTENTIALLY BE TRIGGERING FOR YOU! 
CONTENT CONTAINS DISTURBING ADULT LANGUAGE!
